---
title: Indonesian Pork Meatballs with Noodles, Veggies & Sesame Seeds
description: Put an Asian spin on pork meatballs with kecap manis, sesame oil, ginger and garlic. Then, swap the usual pasta for ramen noodles, add some tasty greens and you've got yourself a new noodle dish that's sure to become a family fave.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e851e621e1cb54bc93d51b2-6c50a519.jpg
